com.devtence.will.dev.commons

Class PushQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.devtence.will.dev.commons.PushQueue

  • public class PushQueue
extends java.lang.Object
    Simple wrapper class for accessing the Google AppEngine TaskQueue, in order to create new queue methods it is required to declare the queues in the queue.xml file inside the project. For more info on this please read https://cloud.google.com/appengine/docs/java/taskqueue/push/creating-push-queues
    Since:
    2016-04-01
    Author:
    plessmann
